import React, { Component } from 'react'; class ExploreTwo extends Component { state = { data: { "preHeading": "Exclusive Assets", "heading": "Explore Our Collection", "btn_1": "View All", "btn_2": "Load More", "exploreData": [ { "id": "1", "img": "/img/auction_1.jpg", "title": "EIGHT", "owner": "Local Richard", "price": "1.5 ETH", "count": "1 of 1", "btnText": "Place a Local Bid" }, { "id": "2", "img": "/img/auction_2.jpg", "title": "Domain Names (Local)", "owner": "Local John", "price": "2.7 ETH", "count": "1 of 1", "btnText": "Place a Local Bid" }, { "id": "3", "img": "/img/auction_3.jpg", "title": "Trading Cards", "owner": "Arham", "price": "2.3 ETH", "count": "1 of 1", "btnText": "Place a Bid" }, { "id": "4", "img": "/img/auction_4.jpg", "title": "Industrial Revolution", "owner": "Yasmin", "price": "1.8 ETH", "count": "1 of 1", "btnText": "Place a Bid" } ] } }; render() { return (
{/* Intro */}
{this.state.data.preHeading}

{this.state.data.heading}

{this.state.data.btn_1}
{this.state.data.exploreData.map((item, idx) => { return (
{/* Single Item */}
{item.title}
Owned By
{item.owner}
{item.price} {item.count}
{item.btnText}
); })}
{this.state.data.btn_2}
); } } export default ExploreTwo;
